Title: Separation of variables for the quantum relativistic Toda lattices
Authors: V.B.Kuznetsov and A.V.Tsiganov
Comments: 13 pp., AMSTex, Report 94-07, Mathematical preprint series,
  University of Amsterdam
\\
  We consider quantum analogs of the relativistic Toda lattices and give new
$2\times 2$ $L$-operators for these models. Making use of the variable
separation the spectral problem for the quantum integrals of motion is reduced
to solving one-dimensional separation equations.
